# Refine Typedealer for Banners

The goal is to differentiate the `typedealer` URL parameter for banner links depending on their position (middle, bottom, right/sticky) without adding new parameters, just by extending the `typedealer` string.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will map the positions as follows:
> - Middle Banner (`.banner-middle`) -> `_banner_middle`
> - Bottom Banner (`.banner-bottom`) -> `_banner_bottom`
> - Sidebar Banner (`.sticky-banner`) -> `_banner_right`
> - Others -> No suffix (keeps `organic_{slug}`)

